&gt; [{quoted}](name=Loote,realm=OCE,application-id=Ntey9fRZ,discussion-id=0cAFbB9J,comment-id=0003,timestamp=2015-11-22T05:40:01.242+0000)
&gt;
&gt; Hey Jason! 
&gt; 
&gt; We&#039;re still working on identifying what specific organisation we&#039;re going to be working with. It&#039;s a bit of an involved process as I want to make sure we pick a reputable organisation, the right cause and making sure that we know what the donation is going to impact. 
&gt; 
&gt; Since we haven&#039;t done this in Oceania before, we&#039;re spending a lot of time researching to make sure we pick the right place. We&#039;re working with some experts from our NA office to help guide us on this. We should have a much better update in the near future. 
&gt; 
&gt; This is absolutely something that we&#039;re following up on and want to make sure it&#039;s done as quickly as possible, but also thoroughly.


This was 21 days ago, and i just went through the red tracker, I&#039;d honestly say the near future has passed.

I hate that I feel the need to consistently bring this up, and if it weren&#039;t for other shotty companies I&#039;d probably have trust in this getting done without the pushing, but this is the world we live in.

At the very least I want us to have an idea of how much was raised.
